    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily errands and weekend trips. It runs smoothly and looks great\u2014definitely ready for its next adventure! I've taken great care of it, and I\u2019d love for it to go to a home where it'll be appreciated just as much. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by and take it for a spin!",
