    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six engine. This unit boasts crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides precise gear engagement, while the factory limited-slip differential ensures optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, addressing key chassis vulnerabilities inherent to the platform. The suspension geometry remains true, offering a balanced, communicative driving experience. This is a well-maintained example of BMW's M-division heritage, ready for the next enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
