    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-cared-for car that balances performance with everyday practicality. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, showing only the minor, superficial stone chips typical of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is clean and inviting; the seating surfaces are firm and well-preserved, and every feature\u2014from the premium audio system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, having followed a strict maintenance schedule with recent fluid changes and a clean bill of health from a certified technician. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the tires offer plenty of life for several seasons to come. It\u2019s a solid, reliable, and attractive vehicle that looks and drives beautifully.",
      "price": 34500.0,
