      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for this absolute gem of a car. It\u2019s been my trusty sidekick and still runs like a total dream! It\u2019s in really wonderful shape\u2014super clean inside and out, with just a tiny bit of honest wear that shows it\u2019s been loved. It\u2019s been super reliable for me, and I know it\u2019s got so many more great miles left in it. If you\u2019re looking for a smooth, comfy ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin! \u2728",
